  {
    "key": "8e4c16623415a017f12b95b42ac51cfb4aefabd0bbc4421df6fe85264e0d4dc5",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_82.png[/img]When you took command of the company it was a ragtag band of men clinging for life, an ad hoc assembly of sellswords stitched together with nothing if not sheer stubbornness and absolute contempt for common sense. Now you watch as the men walk around like frayed revenants of an unworldly wild, their armor adorned with hideous scalps and pelts and bones, the ill-shapen recreation of conquest fitted such that others may know the %companyname% could not be sorted by any measure known to the earth whether it be monster or man.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.SuccessText = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_82.png[/img]When you took command of the company it was a ragtag band of men clinging for life, an ad hoc assembly of sellswords stitched together with nothing if not sheer stubbornness and absolute contempt for common sense. Now you watch as the men walk around like frayed revenants of an unworldly wild, their armor adorned with hideous scalps and pelts and bones, the ill-shapen recreation of conquest fitted such that others may know the %companyname% could not be sorted by any measure known to the earth whether it be monster or man.\""
